 &amp; Rosemary deodorant\nNL: Etos, Albert Heijn, Jumbo, DA, WAAR, Picnic and Dille Chamomile\n\nLavender deodorant\nNL: Etos, Albert Heijn, DA, WAAR, Holland &amp; Barrett, and Dille Chamomile\n\nWoodland deodorant\nNL: Holland &amp; Barrett, WAAR, Dille Chamomile\nBE: Holland &amp; Barrett, Dille Chamomile<\/p>","question_3":"Which countries do you ship to?","answer_3":"<p>We ship to all EU countries (and some non-EU countries). By clicking \"Checkout\" in your shopping cart, you can then select your country. If your country isn't listed, please let us know. We ship your package free of charge within the Netherlands for orders over €35.<\/p>","question_4":"What payment methods can I use?","answer_4":"<p>You can pay with iDeal, PayPal, GPay, ShopPay and your credit card.\/p&gt;<\/p>","question_5":"","answer_5":"","question_6":"","answer_6":"","question_7":"","answer_7":"","question_8":"","answer_8":"","question_9":"","answer_9":"","question_10":"","answer_10":""}}},"block_order":["paragraph_aMkfUp"],"custom_css":[".faqs .faqs-item .card-header .title {color: #2b2b2b; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0px; font-weight: 500; background: #f8f4f0; padding: 5px 0px; border-top: none; border-bottom: 1px solid #f84d27;}","faqs-item#FaqsSection-template--26621760274781__faqs_6mziiU {background-color: #f9f5f1;}",".faqs-item .collapse {background: #f8f4f0; color: #000; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; border: none;}",".faqs .faqs-item .card-header:not(.collapsed) .title:after {transform: scale(0); transform-origin: left;}"],"name":"t:sections.faqs.presets.name","settings":{"container":"1170","padding_full_width":0,"title":"","color_title":"#f4633a","fontsize_title":15,"fontsize_title_mb":16,"mg_bottom_title":12,"mg_bottom_title_mb":12,"enable_border_title":false,"border_color_title":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","description":"","color_des":"#f4633a","fontsize_des":16,"contact_text":"","contact_link":"","contact_color":"#ffffff","contact_color_border":"#ef6454","contact_color_bg":"#ef6